public class StructuredDiscriminatorFlow
extends PredefinedStructuredFlow
implements StructuredDiscriminatorFlow

A structured flow whose initial step is a parallel flow and whose final step is a discriminator flow. Meets the Structured Discriminator pattern (WFP9).
